Committee Democrats offered four commonsense amendments to
improve the bill, but Republicans rejected them all.
Ms. Goodlander offered an amendment to require organizations
to list the name, address, telephone number, and email of the small
businesses they are filing a petition on behalf of with Advocacy.
The commonsense amendment would close a loophole in the bill
that allows powerful trade associations to exploit the process by fil-
